QuestData.Title: Up Against It
QuestData.Description:
We must move quickly if we are to find safety for our people.
This cave is barely defensible, and much of our army is in an even more precarious position.
Let's search deeper.
QuestData.LogDescription: Move deeper into Nazjatar with Jaina and Genn.

Objectives.Objective: Move ahead with Jaina and Genn
